==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pivotal
<hw>Piv"ot*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to
a pivot or turning point; belonging to, or constituting, a pivot; of the
nature of a pivot; <as>as, the <ex>pivotal</ex>opportunity of a career;
the <ex>pivotal</ex> position in a battle.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

